@startuml case-lifecycle
title Case (Intervention) Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Created by Vertical Representative

Draft --> Submitted : PII Captured & Evidence Attached
Submitted --> Verified : Verification Officer Confirms Integrity

state Verified {
  [*] --> ReadyForActivation
}

Verified --> Active : Program Manager Approves Enrollment
Active --> Suspended : Consent Withdrawn / Geo-Reorg / Policy Breach
Suspended --> Active : Remedy Applied / Consent Renewed

state Active {
  [*] --> Stabilized : Objectives Met (Final Assessment)
}

Stabilized --> Closed : Manual Closure by Vertical Owner
Closed --> Reopened : Exceptional Appeal Approved
Reopened --> Active

Closed --> Archived : Retained after Retention Period
Archived --> [*]

@enduml
